      <note xml:id="q-847d5d94-362c-e311-93c1-000bdb5cc6d5" type="heading1" n="1">My <sic>Parst</sic><corr>Past</corr></note>
      <u xml:id="q-857d5d94-362c-e311-93c1-000bdb5cc6d5" who="R" n="2">When I left
				school I took an <sic>exsam</sic><corr>exam</corr> at Chetham dock yard In July.</u>
      <u xml:id="q-867d5d94-362c-e311-93c1-000bdb5cc6d5" who="R" n="3">I took it twice
				because I failed the first time.</u>
      <u xml:id="q-877d5d94-362c-e311-93c1-000bdb5cc6d5" who="R" n="4">The second time I
				<sic>parst</sic><corr>passed</corr>.</u>
      <u xml:id="q-887d5d94-362c-e311-93c1-000bdb5cc6d5" who="R" n="5">Because I had
				<sic>parst</sic><corr>passed</corr> I was employed at the dock yard has an <sic>aprentes</sic><corr>apprentice</corr> for two years as an
				<sic>electrion</sic><corr>electrician</corr>.</u>
      <u xml:id="q-897d5d94-362c-e311-93c1-000bdb5cc6d5" who="R" n="6">After my
				<sic>aprentaship</sic><corr>apprenticeship</corr> was up I stayed at the dock yard for a couple of years.</u>
    </body>
